[normal] 
[normal]UK
[normal] participates in a number
[normal] of g
[normal]overnment schemes
[normal] available in 
[normal]Northern Ireland
[normal] designed to help 
[normal]boost
[normal] the economic
[normal] recovery. Thes
[normal]e include: 
