[normal]&#xa0;[bold]The lack of available data means that it is difficult to properly assess the impact of the reduced availability of cred[bold]it in NI, and also means that there is not sufficient visibility about whether banks are reaching their agreed lending targets. [bold]&#xa0;[bold]4.1.
