[normal]&#xa0;[bold]Following the closure of [bold]Danske[bold] Bank of some branches in rural areas, are the interests of those living in more rural areas, particularly the elderly, sufficiently fulfilled by the banking structure as it currently stands? [bold]&#xa0;[bold]5.1.
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]Santander
[normal] 
[normal]UK
[normal] will have 31 branc
[normal]hes in 
[normal]Northern Ireland
[normal] by the end of this year. This includes 22 branches which we would consider to be in rural areas
[normal].
[normal] We have no plans to reduce 
[normal]the number of branches in 
[normal]Northern Ireland
[normal] below
[normal] this number. 
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]5.2.
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]Santander
[normal] 
[normal]UK
[normal] understands the importance of the branch network to our customers. While 
[normal]Santander
[normal] has closed 6 branches in 
[normal]Northern Ireland
[normal] over the last 18 months, it is important to note that every one of the branches has been in a financial centre where we have at le
[normal]ast one other branch remaining.
[normal] 
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]5.3.
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]Santander
[normal] 
[normal]UK
[normal] is an amalgamation of the ex Abbey, Bradford and Bingley and 
[normal]Alliance
[normal] and Leicester Building Societies and as such we have a number of high streets where we have multiple branches
[normal].
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]5.4.
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]Where we have closed branc
[normal]hes, the customer facing 
[normal]staff have
[normal] all transferred to the remaining branches in the area which we have, in turn, improved to accommodate all of our customers in the town.
[normal] 
[normal]This exercise has shown us that we are able to provide a better service to our cust
[normal]omers when we consol
[normal]idate all of our staff into one, larger 
[normal]branch.
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]5.5.
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]Alongside our branch network, 
[normal]Santander
[normal] has an active “
[normal]omni
[normal]-channel” strategy to ensure that our customers can access our services in a variety of ways as suits their needs. This includes large domestic call 
[normal]centres
[normal] for phone inquiries, a comprehensive online banking platform and a mobile banki
[normal]ng app which was recently named best personal banking app in its category by mobile developer 
[normal]Xtreme
[normal] Labs.
